Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's erupting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right there! Who \Ncares about the needles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this? The \NTransponder Snail is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?! You have a stomachache?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! That's an emergency signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pick it up, can we hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than 50 percent of \Nemergency signals are fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My colleagues are getting \Ncut one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai are gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, what's your name?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody please help me! I'm on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Punk Hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place. The name matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were probably not people's houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there were some kind \Nof Government facilities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Does it actually exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a mythical creature! \NThere's no way that it's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at those features...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it could be anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Battle in the Heat! Luffy \Nvs. The Giant Dragon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cool is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be so impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I like how he snarls, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're hearing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:07:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not even sure it's a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's hard to believe but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it has a lizard-like \Nbody with giant wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks exactly how it's described in myths.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:08:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He breathed fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This creature is unreal! Am I dreaming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's well-armored!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:09:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't provoke him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense your presence-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dragon just said something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra Tiger Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He's so strong and durable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard him talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it too! But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu! Are you people allies \Nof the Seven Warlords too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Warlords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna breathe fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right above us! We can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep making good desserts for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's change our perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend that you're in a sauna. \NIt feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am breaking out in a super sweat of cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky above the island is divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One half is burning hot and \Nthe other is freezing cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Luffy and the others are not melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I feel faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel lightheaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's heat stroke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what they call de-cola-ration?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I'm losing it too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot and that dragon \Nsaid something again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "the Seven Warlords."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have something against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Leave him up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut him up this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me knock him down first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu! It's strange but it's cool here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu! The flames are cool-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, not there! It tickles-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's stuck in the dragon's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What's going on up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the talking voice was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat your own wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack - Green Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:19:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trampolia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lion Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This dragon looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can grill it with the fire on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I made a cold crepe \Nwith the Giant Shellfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll pair nicely with champagne...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are they sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I inhaled too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gas made them sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a natural phenomenon, \Nindigenous to the New World?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did somebody sneak into the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope those four
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that went to the island took a \NBaby Transponder Snail with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to let them know... somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that they're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will care if they go missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take them to the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and crew have saved \Nsomeone from the dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they are extremely shocked\Nwhen they see his bizarre appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Sanji and the others\N have been captured by someone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are locked in a mysterious room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is there that they see an unbelievable sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Straw Hats Stunned! Enter: A \NSamurai's Horrifying Severed Head!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
